{"type":null,"faqId":37079,"title":"如何使用手环检测单次运动数据？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>点亮手环屏幕，滑动至单次运动界面</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121729\" style=\"width:0.33333334in;height:0.40625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，点击开始图标，保持倒计时3s,手环将会检测您单次的运动数据。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121730\" style=\"width:0.275in;height:0.22847222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>：停止计时</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121731\" style=\"width:0.28125in;height:0.21875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>：继续计时</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121732\" style=\"width:0.28125in;height:0.19791667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>：查看此次运动时长、运动数据及消耗的卡路里</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2243","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":24,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,单次运动,单次运动数据检测","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}